<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background: #0d1b2a;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px
        }

        .card {
            background: #162032;
            max-width: 560px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #243447;
            overflow: hidden
        }

        .header {
            background: #1e2e42;
            padding: 28px 32px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #c9a84c
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            color: #fff
        }

        .logo span {
            color: #c9a84c
        }

        .body {
            padding: 32px
        }

        h2 {
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 0 0 12px
        }

        p {
            color: #8a9ab0;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin: 0 0 16px
        }

        .info {
            background: #0d1b2a;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid #243447
        }

        .info table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse
        }

        .info td {
            padding: 6px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #8a9ab0
        }

        .info td:first-child {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #c9a84c;
            width: 120px
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 20px 32px;
            font-size: 11px;
            color: #4a5a6a;
            border-top: 1px solid #243447
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo"><span>TIG</span>CAP Portal</div>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
            <h2>Customer Account Created</h2>
            <p>You have successfully created a client account on TIGCAP. Here is a summary:</p>
            <div class="info">
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Client Name</td>
                        <td>
                            <%= customerFirstName %>
                                <%= customerLastName %>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Client Email</td>
                        <td>
                            <%= customerEmail %>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Client User ID</td>
                        <td><strong>
                                <%= customerUserId %>
                            </strong></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>Created</td>
                        <td>
                            <%= new Date().toLocaleString('en-GB') %>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
            <p>The client has been sent their login credentials separately. You can track their form progress from your
                dashboard.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> The Insolvency Group.</div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>